,750.126\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{decrease}}  3.29%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | 38,558.769\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | 41,070.880\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | 163.0546<br>(30 Jun)\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{decrease}} 236.478\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{decrease}} 251.884\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | 216.565\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{decrease}} $1,091.95\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{decrease}} $1,163.09\n|}\n\n=== Industrial sector ===\n{{Main|Industry of Pakistan}}\n{{See also|Textile industry in Pakistan}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!\n! List\n! FY 2004\n! FY 2005\n! FY 2006\n! FY 2007\n! FY 2008\n! FY 2009\n! FY 2010\n! FY 2011\n! FY 2012\n! FY 2013\n! FY 2014\n! FY 2015\n! FY 2016\n! FY 2017\n! FY 2018 <small>(R)</small>\n! FY 2019 <small>(P)</small>\n|-\n| 6\n| Industrial sector growth rate<br />&nbsp;<ref name=\"pbs#2\" /><ref name=\":4\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.finance.gov.pk/survey/chapters_18/01-Growth.pdf|title=Manufacturing|last=|first=|date=|website=Pakistan Finance Division|access-date=2018-04-28}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |  17.37%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{decrease}}  6.51%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{decrease}}  3.63%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{increase}}  7.73%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{increase}}  8.47%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{decrease}} -5.21%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{increase}}  3.42%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{increase}}  4.51%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{decrease}}  2.55%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{decrease}}  0.75%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{increase}}  4.53%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{increase}}  5.18%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{increase}}  5.69%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{decrease}}  4.55%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{increase}}  4.92%\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | {{decrease}}  1.40%\n|-\n| 6A\n| Mining and Quarrying sector growth rate<br />&nbsp;<ref name